<li><cite id="CITEREFRenker1998" class="citation book cs1">Renker, Elizabeth (1998). <i>Strike Through the Mask: Herman Melville and the Scene of Writing</i>. Baltimore: Johns Hopkins University Press. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-8018-5875-8" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-8018-5875-8"><bdi>978-0-8018-5875-8</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Strike+Through+the+Mask%3A+Herman+Melville+and+the+Scene+of+Writing&amp;rft.place=Baltimore&amp;rft.pub=Johns+Hopkins+University+Press&amp;rft.date=1998&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-8018-5875-8&amp;rft.aulast=Renker&amp;rft.aufirst=Elizabeth&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHerman+Melville" class="Z3988"></span></li>
